Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
current_design(25.10)                                    current_design(25.10)

Name
       current_design  - Changes the current directory in the design hierarchy
       to the specified design and returns the path to the design

Syntax
       current_design

       [-help]

       [<design_name>]

       Changes the current directory in the design hierarchy to the  specified
       design and returns the path to the design.

       If no design is specified, the command returns the top-level design.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

       <design_name>
              Specifies the name of the top design.

Related Information
              * set_max_transition

              * set_min_capacitance

              * set_min_transition

